title: Vegan Gains vs. Plant Eats vs. Canadian Culture.
description: The critique of Canadian culture (and how this presents a problem for organizing the vegan movement (or ANY KIND of movement) in Canada) begins around 7:00 …many of you might prefer to start the tape at around that point.  :-/
